Title: Stereo Delay - VST Plugin
Description: Stereo Delay - it's a VST plugin. Independent delay line for both channels. You can control delay time (up to 1s), low pass filter and panorama for delay signal

Stereo Delay - it's a VST plugin. Independent delay line for both channels. You can control delay time (up to 1s), low pass filter and panorama for delay signal

Created with JUCE Framework, VST SDK 2.4 and MSVC++.
